kehabisan makanan lagi!

826
00:44:54,511 --> 00:44:57,013
Mereka benar-benar menyasarkan pancit,
harap awak tak panjang umur!

827
00:44:57,722 --> 00:44:58,640
Adakah ini?

828
00:45:01,977 --> 00:45:03,061
